    <question>
      <text>Minimize Z = 200x + 500y subject to x + 2y &gt;= 10, 3x + 4y &lt;= 24, x &gt;= 0, y &gt;= 0. Feasible region exists? Check points:</text>
      <option id="A">Yes, corner points (4,3), (0,5), (0,6), (8,0)? No, check intersections.</option>

